# Modules in Different Files

You can split a module into its own file.

```
src/
├── lib.rs           // declares `pub mod front_of_house;`
└── front_of_house/
    └── hosting.rs   // declares `pub fn add_to_waitlist()`
```

```rust
// lib.rs
pub mod front_of_house;

// front_of_house/hosting.rs
pub fn add_to_waitlist() {}
```

> **Note:** File tree mirrors the module tree. Use `pub use` to re-export.
